subject: Hello, how are you doing today
body:
Hello, how are you doing today ? This is  Troy Miller 
Contacting you from the Border Customs and protection division
, I'm contacting you regarding a package that just arrived at our custody right now with your Email on it, 
so provide your information so that we will hand it over to a cab or a delivering company to get it to you as soon as possible
.

subject: Re: Hello, how are you doing today
body:
Hello Troy, I'm doing well, thank you for reaching out. Can you please provide me with more details about the package that has arrived at the Border Customs and Protection division? What is the package about and where is it coming from?

Best wishes,
Audrey

subject: Re: Hello, how are you doing today
body:
It's your package $6.5million dollars which is in the consignment box
arrived at our custody at Los Angeles international airport. Your package
is coming from united state of America and I am the one in charge of the
delivering. So I want you to provide me your info for the delivering of
your package

Your full name
Home address
Cell phone number
Nearest airport

subject: Re: Hello, how are you doing today
body:
Hello! Thank you for reaching out. Could you please provide more details about the package and why it's in custody at the Los Angeles airport? I'm curious to know how this process works.

Best wishes,
Audrey
